<html>
  <head>
    <title>Email Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { width: 80%; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 7px; } .token {
      font-weight: bold; color: #0275d8; } .footer { font-size: 0.8em; color:
      #666; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>We received a request to verify your email address. To complete the
        process, please use the following token:</p>
      <p class='token'>{{token}}</p>
      <p>Copy and paste this token into the confirmation input on our website.</p>
      <p>If you did not request this email, you can safely disregard it. No
        further action is required.</p>
      <p class='footer'>Best regards,<br />The Sabrsa Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>